nodes.label: message
nodes.text: Hi Person1, Thanks for reaching out. Here are the instructions for taking the 4 mg Dexamethasone: Take 5 tablets (20 mg) 12 hours before chemotherapy then take 5 more tablets 6 hours before. So for an approximate 9:30 start, please take 5 at 9:30 pm MM/DD/YYYY then again take 5 at 3:30 in the morning. :(  So rry! Let me know if any clarification is needed. Sincerely, Person2
